  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个金融科技系统的架构图，核心是交易队列和账本服务之间的交互。我打算分成两个主要模块：一个是服务智能合约区域，处理支付和扣费逻辑；另一个是提现区域，处理资金流出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "service smart contract",
        "withdrawal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。服务智能合约区域里，我注意到您提到了µpay，这个是TransactionQueue的别名吗？还有AuthVault在这个区域里扮演什么角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，µpay就是TransactionQueue的简写代号。AuthVault在这里是User0，代表用户账户的认证信息，它会向µpay发起扣费请求，dt=-0.1表示扣除0.1个单位。同时Service0也会向µpay充值，dt=+0.1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User0",
        "µpay",
        "Service0",
        "dt = -0.1",
        "dt = +0.1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在service smart contract子图里添加了µpay节点，User0用虚线连接µpay标注dt=-0.1，Service0也用虚线连接标注dt=+0.1。我还给µpay设置了#626的紫色样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "User0",
        "Service0",
        "style µpay"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来，µpay需要输出到两个方向：一个是User1代表的PaymentGateway，另一个是Service1代表的FraudDetection。这两个都是虚线连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "User1",
        "Service1",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：User1是PaymentGateway，Service1是FraudDetection，都从µpay引出虚线。我注意到User1在后面的withdrawal区域还会再次出现，角色会变成AuthVault对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
        "Service1",
        "withdrawal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，User1在withdrawal区域身份切换为AuthVault，这是同一个实体在不同场景下的不同职能体现。现在说withdrawal区域，核心是tx3，也就是LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
        "tx3",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "withdrawal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已创建withdrawal子图，tx3作为核心节点，设置了#844的深红色样式。User1（此时为AuthVault）和Service1（此时为PaymentGateway）都用虚线连接到tx3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tx3",
