    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我再看一下，Service1在两个子图里标签不同——前面是FraudDetection，后面是PaymentGateway，这样会不会混淆？要不要调整？",
      "elements_involved": [
