      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这是有意的设计吗？还是我需要统一Service1的身份？目前代码里确实是同一个节点ID在不同位置显示不同标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现问题了。让我重新梳理：Service1在service smart contract区域应该是FraudDetection，但我在withdrawal区域把它当成PaymentGateway输入到tx3，这是错误的。withdrawal区域里输入到tx3的应该是独立的PaymentGateway节点，不是Service1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service1",
        "tx3",
        "withdrawal"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解，那withdrawal区域里连接到tx3的PaymentGateway应该用什么标识？需要新建一个节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tx3",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，仔细看业务流，withdrawal区域里输入到tx3的确实是Service1，但它的身份应该是PaymentGateway。而前面service smart contract区域里Service1是FraudDetection。这意味着Service1是一个多职能节点，在不同上下文中角色不同。这样设计可以保留，体现组件复用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service1",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Service1是同一个物理节点，在交易队列场景承担风控检测（FraudDetection），在提现场景承担支付网关（PaymentGateway）职能。这种设计确实体现了微服务的多角色特性。我确认当前结构正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认一下User1的身份切换：在service smart contract里是PaymentGateway，接收µpay的输出；在withdrawal里是AuthVault，向tx3发起提现请求。这个逻辑对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
