    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "很好，我整体过一遍：service smart contract区域包含µpay核心，处理User0扣费和Service0充值，输出到User1和Service1；withdrawal区域以tx3为核心，接收User1和Service1输入，输出到User2、Service2和Service3。样式区分清晰，流向合理。可以定稿了。",
